{"tid":1965495,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【久未露面】57歲王傑認老：但我依然不忘初心","createTime":"2020-04-09T13:27:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-21T19:58:05.000Z","uid":35221,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"0b75d5c56885afa82378745b375d6e2a1963ffb2","tid":1965495,"uid":35221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-09T13:27:29.000Z","msg":"【久未露面】57歲王傑認老：但我依然不忘初心 (12:55)<br />\n文章日期：2020年04月09日<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ldy/20200409/s00009/a4f297b7d00b92cc23a3c88bfe22a799.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fldy%2F20200409%2Fs00009%2Fa4f297b7d00b92cc23a3c88bfe22a799.jpg&h=4b6486bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n久未蒲頭的王傑，今晨突然在微博留言。（微博圖片）<br />\n<br />\n憑《幾分傷心幾分痴》、《一無所有》等金曲爆紅的王傑，已有一段時間沒公開露面，就連社交網也甚少更新，現年57歲的王傑，近年已淡出香港樂壇，並轉攻內地市場，今早王傑突然現身微博，並留言說：「我老了...但是我依然不忘初心！思想依然可愛.....心中依然充滿了愛....艱難時期，大家保重....永遠愛你們⋯⋯ ​​​​」惹來不少內地網民留言。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ldy/20200409/s00009/a4f77cf6fc18e83c4f3f9a92db8fb6f4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fldy%2F20200409%2Fs00009%2Fa4f77cf6fc18e83c4f3f9a92db8fb6f4.jpg&h=d5e9b0dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n王傑表示在艱難時間盼大家保重。（微博截圖）<br />\n<br />\n（即時娛樂）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ol.mingpao.com/ldy/showbiz/latest/20200409/1586408544155/【久未露面】57歲王傑認老-但我依然不忘初心\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fol.mingpao.com%2Fldy%2Fshowbiz%2Flatest%2F20200409%2F1586408544155%2F%E3%80%90%E4%B9%85%E6%9C%AA%E9%9C%B2%E9%9D%A2%E3%80%9157%E6%AD%B2%E7%8E%8B%E5%82%91%E8%AA%8D%E8%80%81-%E4%BD%86%E6%88%91%E4%BE%9D%E7%84%B6%E4%B8%8D%E5%BF%98%E5%88%9D%E5%BF%83&d=xid8M%2BhLl0Hh6VuzhHwKVdXdGXproJJDEW77mXnEmng%3D&h=422ae8b8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fol.mingpao.com%2Fldy%2Fshowbiz%2Flatest%2F20200409%2F1586408544155%2F%E3%80%90%E4%B9%85%E6%9C%AA%E9%9C%B2%E9%9D%A2%E3%80%9157%E6%AD%B2%E7%8E%8B%E5%82%91%E8%AA%8D%E8%80%81-%E4%BD%86%E6%88%91%E4%BE%9D%E7%84%B6%E4%B8%8